{"data":{"metadata":{"publishedAt":"2023-07-15","updatedAt":"2026-02-07","featured":false},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","body":[{"type":"textBody","value":"Hello! I'm Asuka. I love creating things.","style":"plain"}]},{"type":"paragraph","body":[{"type":"textBody","value":"Currently I work at ","style":"plain"},{"type":"link","body":[{"type":"textBody","value":"LY Corporation","style":"plain"}],"url":"https://www.lycorp.co.jp/en/"},{"type":"textBody","value":" as a front-end developer, building web (and occasionally native) applications used by millions of users.","style":"plain"}]},{"type":"paragraph","body":[{"type":"textBody","value":"During work I mainly focus on helping my team to create more value more efficiently while being happier.","style":"plain"}]},{"type":"paragraph","body":[{"type":"textBody","value":"I believe the most important thing to learn is the ability to learn and reflect, and everyday I strive to embody that and make myself a better human than I was yesterday.","style":"plain"}]},{"type":"heading","level":1,"body":[{"type":"textBody","value":"About me","style":"plain"}]},{"type":"paragraph","body":[{"type":"textBody","value":"Video gaming has always been my biggest passion since I was a child, and game design is the reason I fell in love with programming.","style":"plain"}]},{"type":"paragraph","body":[{"type":"textBody","value":"I speak fluent Mandarin, Japanese and English. Out of these three, English is my favorite. At the moment I'm learning Spanish, aiming to become proficient in three of the world's most widely spoken languages.","style":"plain"}]},{"type":"paragraph","body":[{"type":"textBody","value":"I've always had a deep passion for expressing myself through turning my ideas into reality, which is the major reason why I'm into web development. I also enjoy ","style":"plain"},{"type":"link","body":[{"type":"textBody","value":"writing","style":"plain"}],"url":"https://asukawang.com/blog/"},{"type":"textBody","value":" and photography.","style":"plain"}]},{"type":"paragraph","body":[{"type":"textBody","value":"I love making ","style":"plain"},{"type":"link","body":[{"type":"textBody","value":"lists","style":"plain"}],"url":"https://asukawang.com/list"},{"type":"textBody","value":", so I'll tell you more about myself with lists below:","style":"plain"}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"body":[{"type":"textBody","value":"Favorite Games","style":"plain"}]},{"type":"list","ordered":false,"items":[{"type":"listItem","body":[{"type":"textBody","value":"Warcraft III","style":"plain"}]},{"type":"listItem","body":[{"type":"textBody","value":"League of Legends","style":"plain"}]},{"type":"listItem","body":[{"type":"textBody","value":"Wrath of the Lich King","style":"plain"}]},{"type":"listItem","body":[{"type":"textBody","value":"Hades","style":"plain"}]},{"type":"listItem","body":[{"type":"textBody","value":"and many more","style":"plain"}]}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"body":[{"type":"textBody","value":"Favorite Movie, Drama, Book and Song","style":"plain"}]},{"type":"list","ordered":false,"items":[{"type":"listItem","body":[{"type":"textBody","value":"La La Land","style":"plain"}]},{"type":"listItem","body":[{"type":"textBody","value":"Narcos Season 1","style":"plain"}]},{"type":"listItem","body":[{"type":"textBody","value":"Dragon Raja","style":"plain"}]},{"type":"listItem","body":[{"type":"textBody","value":"Lose Yourself","style":"plain"}]}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"body":[{"type":"textBody","value":"Next Travel Destination Candidates","style":"plain"}]},{"type":"list","ordered":false,"items":[{"type":"listItem","body":[{"type":"textBody","value":"New York City, United States","style":"plain"}]},{"type":"listItem","body":[{"type":"textBody","value":"Denver, United States","style":"plain"}]},{"type":"listItem","body":[{"type":"textBody","value":"Amsterdam, Netherlands","style":"plain"}]},{"type":"listItem","body":[{"type":"textBody","value":"Krakow, Poland","style":"plain"}]}]},{"type":"heading"